    <section id="import-auto-idm376976048">
      <title>Problems and Mistakes on Site</title>
      <para id="import-auto-idm696213744">.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm320939936">Construction sites may have many different problems. For example, sites can have problems with noise, dust, dirt and mud. Construction materials may also be a target for thieves. The cleanliness of the site facilities can also be a major problem on a building site. Problems can also exist with work that has already been completed. The construction worker must therefore know how to deal with these issues. At the end of this section students should be able to identify and deal with on-site problems and apologize for any mistakes that have occurred. </para>
