          <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 6.png" height="207" width="170"/>
        </media>
      <caption>Leaking toilet. </caption></figure><section id="import-auto-idm378183936">
        <title>Technical terms  </title>
        <para id="import-auto-idm1046189728">.</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm885397248">Match the words with their definitions </para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm380109728">.</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm320237072">A: maintain…………….a waterproof sealant………….. </para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm352217248">B: repair……………….when water comes out of a damaged pipe…………..</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm759584096">C: waste water…………bath, toilets, sinks etc…………..</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm1032363200">D: disposal……………..to keep something in good condition…………..</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm695889936">E: install………………..dirty water from the toilet, sink or bath………….. </para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm756090736">F: mastic………………..to put in (a toilet, sink, bath) …………..</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm1041613424">G: fixtures………………getting rid of waste…………..</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm738496192">H: leak…………………..to fix something…………..</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm684628000">.</para>
